data.description: This beautiful, ranch home is definitely going to check off a lot of boxes for potential buyers!  Enjoy all of the benefits of peaceful, country living, yet your neighbors are still close by.  The main level of the home offers a large living room, eat in kitchen that walks out to a deck and amazing back yard, three nice sized bedrooms and recently updated full bathroom.  The lower level has another full bathroom and large, finished Rec room area.  Outside, the back yard boasts a beautiful gazebo, large storage shed and an additional detached garage/workshop and outbuilding that is sure to please hobbyists and collectors alike.  Recent updates and improvements include metal roof on house in 2013, Gazebo in 2018, newer windows, new toilet in main level bath and new grinder for basement bath toilet, GE kitchen appliances, and the well and septic were both serviced in 2023.  Seller has offered a one-year Ultimate home warranty through Old Republic for additional peace of mind.  Come see and make this your new home for 2024!
